{"tid":1175832,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"六月份Cult片放映會-骨灰級經典Cult《太空英雌芭芭拉 Barbarella》","createTime":"2019-05-28T22:20:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-29T11:39:56.000Z","uid":212112,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"457710b4d5af4e4a12236b8f9d898efcdf0dbcb1","tid":1175832,"uid":212112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T22:20:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ue3f1dE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUe3f1dE.png&h=a4423dd3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n太空英雌芭芭拉 Barbarella &middot; 放映會 Movie Screening<br />\n<br />\nJune 1 ❖ 19:00 - 22:00<br />\n分享 x 電影 x 交流<br />\n<br />\nVenue: <strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">Sacred Space 密宇</span></strong> &infin;&infin;&infin;&infin;&infin;&infin;&infin;&infin;&infin;&infin;&infin;&infin;&infin;&infin;&infin;&infin;&infin;&infin;&infin;&infin;&infin;&infin;&infin;&infin;&infin;&infin;&infin;&infin;<br />\n骨灰級經典Cult《太空英雌芭芭拉 Barbarella》<br />\n-<br />\n影史著名的上世紀60年代科幻小甜Cult片。劇情講述41世紀聯合地球政府的五星巡航員-芭芭拉是專門收服太空星系中的妖魔鬼怪的女版007奉地球總統之命，尋找一名失了蹤的邪惡科學家並阻止他去毀滅地球。<br />\n一次意外她被逼降落在一個星球時，她需要面對SM機器、淫邪的雙性戀皇后、盲眼的英俊天使等人物，亦經歷了種種奇異的冒險，既有追逐打鬥，也有旖旎動人的小甜原素⋯⋯<br />\n-<br />\n日期：1-6-2019<br />\n地點：火炭<br />\n時間 ：19:00-22:00<br />\n-<br />\n❖ 流程<br />\n<br />\n19:00 開放入場/放映暖場作品<br />\n19:30 介紹電影<br />\n19:40 簡述「Cult片」文化<br />\n19:45 欣賞電影《太空英雌芭芭拉》<br />\n21:25 自由交流/分享時間/講者影評 -<br />\n<br />\n此活動名額尚餘20個，<br />\n請於Instagram: <strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">Chat_Cult _Place</span></strong> 查詢/報名<br />\n<br />\n多謝支持<br />\n-<br />\n<br />\n本影片無論是特效、表演、道具還是故事一切從簡，山寨氣息濃厚，Cult 味與後現代感十足，和同年代的《2001太空漫遊》簡直是天與地之差。<br />\n但它也有著它風格華麗，情色與科幻，時尚敏感與漫畫的流暢結合，造型奇特誇張，服飾前衛就算是放到現在仍然時尚，特技雖然粗糙，但是塑料美學和那些畫出來的幕景視覺悅目，融合了艷情、科幻、搞笑、冒險等種種元素<br />\n。<br />\n在影片開頭，性感的女主角大膽地表演了一場在無重狀態中的脫衣艷舞，之後穿著專門為她設計的一件與眾不同的太空衣，性感加曼妙的身段使飾演女主角的Jane Fonda一躍成為當時歐洲的首席明星。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6saJ98Z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6saJ98Z.png&h=3ef0e6b4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q9BJqHj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ9BJqHj.png&h=c79eea24&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pZwtBO0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpZwtBO0.png&h=f1195fe8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w2CgLHm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw2CgLHm.png&h=5494e8c7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V5Uu5Hn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV5Uu5Hn.png&h=e8e0eb96&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VoJDeAJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVoJDeAJ.png&h=24d6002f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/baGxi2o.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbaGxi2o.png&h=b2116ca9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SQ4Gcnp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSQ4Gcnp.png&h=4d28c9b6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b990ebe0b6270aef411cca6c2476e7da934efc7c","tid":1175832,"uid":212112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T22:32:39.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"87e0deafdc98635188211da128fbfd8ef3b9e019","tid":1175832,"uid":212112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T23:03:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c31f204eb94099515cbc7e70c0d52ab6a6dde11","tid":1175832,"uid":212112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T01:47:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c65c4d6e2734c0566f76891c96421628cf35f0ee","tid":1175832,"uid":212112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T03:03:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d03